@startuml TeamConnect-Architecture

title TeamConnect - General Architecture (High-Level)

actor User

package "Frontend" {
  [Angular App\n(UI)] as Angular
}

package "Backend" {
  [TeamConnect.Api\n(ASP.NET Core)] as API
}

database "MongoDB\n(TeamConnectDb)" as DB

cloud "SMTP Server\n(Gmail)" as SMTP
cloud "Jira\n(future integration)" as Jira

User --> Angular
Angular --> API : HTTPS / REST API + JWT
API --> DB : MongoDB Driver
API --> SMTP : Email notifications
API ..> Jira : planned

@enduml
